metadata.name: KINGSHIP
metadata.description:
The man who has authority over his limitations, wants, fears and goals, and has control of himself is greater than a king.

______________________________

A gold-coated digital sculpture created by JohnPaul Val to reflect on the journey he has embarked upon and his desire to become that which he has desired to become.

A tribute to all that desires to rule their kingdom as true Kings.

©️ JOHNPAUL VAL
